- Recording vlogs throughout
- FAERIS in background of vlog post (Book 2)
- Viral exposure, realizes been tracked since Book 1
- Confrontation with Chief Whitford (father)
- Does he know she's Gloom Girl?
- Is he protecting, hunting, or watching?
- Privacy violation + family drama
- Relationship with Leta throughout
- Teleporter in combat

### Chief Whitford
- Corrupt police chief (Book 1)
- FAERIS tracking his own daughter?
- Learning Tess is Gloom Girl (if he doesn't know)
- Confrontation moment
- Redemption possible? Or tragic ending?
