- "Fake news" about evidence linking him to Tank
- Assassination attempt - staged or real?
- Iconic "fist" photo moment
- Blames "Ghost Squad" or CADENS
- Turns self into martyr
- Wins presidency despite/because of everything
- Beginning corruption (Book 2-3)
- Consciousness copy reveal (he's like Ahdia)
- Realization moment (Books 4-6)
- Redemption begins
- Alliance with Ahdia (Book 7)

